<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.7">
<l>ōtu vāymaiyu muvaṉiyap piṟappu muṉakku muṉtanta vantaṇa ṉoruvaṉ</l>
<l>kāta leṉmakaṉ pukaliṭaṅ kāṇēṉ kaṇṭu nītaru vāyeṉak keṉṟu</l>
<l>kōtil vāymaiyi ṉāṉuṉai vēṇṭi yakuṟai muṭittavaṉ ciṟuvaṉaik koṭuttāy</l>
<l>āta lālvantu ṉaṭiyiṇai yaṭaintē ṉaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkat tammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The priest who previously gave you recited chants</l>
<l rend="indent">and [your second] birth of [thread] investiture,</l>
<l>Having said, “I cannot find the place that my beloved son has gone;</l>
<l rend="indent">you search and bring [him] to me,”</l>
<l>Completing the request that the one of faultless truths asked of you,</l>
<l rend="indent">you gave [him] his little one;</l>
<l>Therefore, coming [here], I took refuge at your two feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
